sub_title: Test Automation Engineer // I help in delivering quality software
summary:
Key Skills: PHP, PHPUnit, Laravel, API development and testing, GUI testing with Selenium WebDriver, Automation Framework Development, Python and pytest, Continuous Integration and Continuous Deployment, Object Oriented Programing practices, Web Application Development, JavaScript, Linux/Unix Shell Scripting, HTML, CSS

A firm believer and advocate of Test Driven Development interested in and dedicated to the process of development and delivery of a sound application. Experienced in web application development for more than 8 years, Agile application development practices and implementation of quality assurance practices for more than 5 years. Noted for being quick to learn new technologies, justifying (if applicable) its application towards the benefit of the team and teaching them to team members.

Currently looking for career opportunities to develop professionally in the field of Test Automation, Quality Assurance, meaningful Software Testing and Technical/Functional communication in a progressive Web Applications industry.
